# Files for simple dac.
# This dac is standalone with its own power supply
# Currently, two schematics are used:
# bandgap reference and power
#
schematics bandgap_reference_v0.2.sch dacpower_v0.2.sch
output-name dac_v0.2.project

# After editing schematics:
# gnetlist  -g drc2 bandgap_reference_v0.2.sch -o bgout.txt
# (also use -vv sometimes with gnetlist)
# run gsch2pcb
# to generate .net, .pcb, and .new.pcb files
